    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-10-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-10-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="1345"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1345">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 412.11/32.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Ambassador</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-10-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 9, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Foreign Office agrees to extend time for filing claims of American claimants,
                    but does not desire to extend this privilege beyond American claims and
                    therefore requests that any of these not already presented to the Commission be
                    transmitted to the Foreign Office, which will thereupon bring them before the
                    Commission in such a manner as not to permit the right of filing to some ten
                    thousand Mexican claimants, consideration of which can be prevented by this
                    method.</p>
                <p>In view of the fact that three quarters of the American claims have not been
                    filed with the Commission, I request instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
